      <title>如何“偷懒”：从提升代码质量开始</title>
      <link>https://hitzhangjie.github.io/blog/2020-10-16-%E5%A7%94%E5%A9%89%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%B4%A7%E8%BF%AB%E6%80%A7/</link>
